834
00:52:00,680 --> 00:52:03,750
And he still is.

835
00:52:03,760 --> 00:52:05,170
Don't go.

836
00:52:06,060 --> 00:52:08,050
Come to my wedding.

837
00:52:08,060 --> 00:52:09,950
It's my wedding.

838
00:52:29,950 --> 00:52:31,340
Are you crazy?

839
00:52:31,350 --> 00:52:33,210
Why are you going through my phone?

840
00:52:33,220 --> 00:52:34,610
You have no class.

841
00:52:43,220 --> 00:52:44,750
Can we talk?

842
00:52:50,260 --> 00:52:52,110
Yes, honey.

843
00:52:52,120 --> 00:52:54,040
I just washed my face.

844
00:52:54,060 --> 00:52:55,850
What are you doing on Christmas?

845
00:52:55,850 --> 00:52:57,040
Nothing much.

846
00:52:57,060 --> 00:52:59,220
You're not having a party with your kids?

847
00:52:59,220 --> 00:53:01,170
Things are too crazy for that.

848
00:53:01,180 --> 00:53:04,640
Then want to have a party, just you and me?

849
00:53:04,660 --> 00:53:07,570
A party? Really?

850
00:53:08,760 --> 00:53:11,550
Okay. Honey, I'll see you tomorrow.

851
00:53:15,120 --> 00:53:16,810
Oh, you scared me.,

852
00:53:16,830 --> 00:53:19,020
Why were you eavesdropping?

853
00:53:19,030 --> 00:53:20,320
How rude.

854
00:53:22,720 --> 00:53:24,480
We need to talk.

855
00:53:24,490 --> 00:53:26,170
About what?

856
00:53:26,180 --> 00:53:27,710
Come with me.

857
00:53:37,930 --> 00:53:39,550
What is it?

858
00:53:39,560 --> 00:53:42,320
It's cold.
Why do we have to talk out here?

859
00:53:43,390 --> 00:53:47,020
Your parents will hear us if we talk at home.

860
00:53:48,120 --> 00:53:49,520
What is it?

861
00:53:54,290 --> 00:53:56,220
Be honest with me.

862
00:53:56,220 --> 00:53:57,270
About what?

863
00:53:57,290 --> 00:53:58,280
Who is he?

864
00:53:58,290 --> 00:53:59,280
Who do you mean?

865
00:53:59,290 --> 00:54:00,850
The man you were on the phone with.

866
00:54:00,850 --> 00:54:02,880
It wasn't a he. It was a friend.

867
00:54:02,890 --> 00:54:04,110
What's wrong with you?

868
00:54:04,120 --> 00:54:05,210
Are you cheating on me?

869
00:54:05,220 --> 00:54:06,570
Why would I cheat on you?

870
00:54:06,580 --> 00:54:07,810
You stay out all night,

871
00:54:07,830 --> 00:54:10,050
and you get secret text messages.

872
00:54:10,060 --> 00:54:11,480
It's not normal.

873
00:54:11,490 --> 00:54:12,920
Are you seeing someone?

874
00:54:12,930 --> 00:54:14,840
You must be crazy.

875
00:54:14,850 --> 00:54:17,210
How can I be seeing a man?

876
00:54:17,220 --> 00:54:19,520
You know how busy I am with work.

877
00:54:19,530 --> 00:54:21,210
Are you losing your mind?

878
00:54:21,220 --> 00:54:22,340
You should see a doctor.

879
00:54:22,350 --> 00:54:24,610
I will if I have to,

880
00:54:24,620 --> 00:54:25,650
so be honest with me.

881
00:54:25,660 --> 00:54:28,020
Your condition looks really serious.

882
00:54:28,030 --> 00:54:29,820
I can come home late when I have lots of work,

883
00:54:29,830 --> 00:54:31,250
and I can come home in the morning

884
00:54:31,260 --> 00:54:32,980
after taking a trip outside the city.

885
00:54:32,990 --> 00:54:34,610
Why would you eavesdrop?

886
00:54:34,620 --> 00:54:36,480
And you call yourself a man?

887
00:54:36,490 --> 00:54:37,670
You have no class.

888
00:54:37,680 --> 00:54:39,870
Don't try to turn me into a psychopath.

889
00:54:39,890 --> 00:54:42,020
Or a man with no class.

890
00:54:42,030 --> 00:54:44,250
You don't call a friend honey and kiss her.

891
00:54:44,260 --> 00:54:47,070
Woman do that with friends.

892
00:54:47,080 --> 00:54:48,750
Don't pick a fight with me like this.

893
00:54:48,760 --> 00:54:50,440
You should go see a doctor tomorrow.

894
00:54:50,450 --> 00:54:51,810
You need to quit your job.

895
00:54:52,580 --> 00:54:53,440
What?

896
00:54:53,450 --> 00:54:55,070
Quit it right now!

897
00:54:55,720 --> 00:54:57,270
I don't believe this.

898
00:54:57,290 --> 00:54:59,280
Just who do you think you are?

899
00:54:59,290 --> 00:55:02,920
You brought me here in the cold to tell me that?

900
00:55:02,930 --> 00:55:04,550
Unbelievable.

901
00:55:04,560 --> 00:55:06,580
I want a divorce, then.

902
00:55:06,580 --> 00:55:08,040
What?

903
00:55:08,060 --> 00:55:10,380
Are you scared?

904
00:55:10,390 --> 00:55:13,070
Then stop doing stuff like this.

905
00:55:16,160 --> 00:55:18,180
You think I'm an idiot?

906
00:55:18,180 --> 00:55:22,210
I have pride and I can be stubborn.

907
00:55:22,220 --> 00:55:24,040
So?

908
00:55:24,060 --> 00:55:29,080
You know how hard I'm trying here?

909
00:55:29,080 --> 00:55:30,920
To protect this family,

910
00:55:30,930 --> 00:55:36,420
for Aeji and Jungji, I'm being so patient.

911
00:55:36,430 --> 00:55:41,520
Whatever you were doing, stop it.

912
00:55:41,530 --> 00:55:45,440
I can forgive you this once.

913
00:55:46,290 --> 00:55:48,150
Who do you think you are?

914
00:55:48,160 --> 00:55:50,840
I'm still your husband.

915
00:55:50,850 --> 00:55:56,150
Whatever happens next,

916
00:55:56,160 --> 00:55:59,450
it won't be my responsibility.

917
00:56:06,530 --> 00:56:07,650
You're leaving already?

918
00:56:07,660 --> 00:56:09,110
Yes.

919
00:56:09,120 --> 00:56:11,040
Eat first. I'll whip something up for you.

920
00:56:11,060 --> 00:56:13,150
It's okay. I'll see you later.

921
00:56:16,530 --> 00:56:18,320
What is it?

922
00:56:18,330 --> 00:56:22,150
It's Minjung.
He's been skipping breakfast.

923
00:56:22,160 --> 00:56:25,420
Sometimes he looks okay,
other times unhappy.

924
00:56:25,430 --> 00:56:28,380
It must be because of work.

925
00:56:28,390 --> 00:56:30,650
Parcel service is hard work.

926
00:57:08,830 --> 00:57:10,450
Hurry up!

927
00:57:14,660 --> 00:57:16,020
Have a nice day.

928
00:57:17,560 --> 00:57:18,680
Buy groceries with this.

929
00:57:19,720 --> 00:57:22,210
Did you see the delivered vegetables?

930
00:57:22,220 --> 00:57:23,610
I didn't.

931
00:57:24,720 --> 00:57:26,270
We get this every week,

932
00:57:26,290 --> 00:57:27,550
so don't buy vegetables.

933
00:57:27,560 --> 00:57:29,280
Just get a bit of meat, fish and fruit.

934
00:57:29,290 --> 00:57:31,420
Don't buy too much at once.

935
00:57:31,430 --> 00:57:35,480
I'll take care of this so you go to work.

936
00:57:35,490 --> 00:57:38,520
Don't drink too much.
Come home early.

937
00:58:15,620 --> 00:58:18,150
Hobak, why are you getting so many texts?

938
00:58:18,160 --> 00:58:19,220
Are they spam?

939
00:58:19,220 --> 00:58:22,440
They are worse than spam.

940
00:58:33,260 --> 00:58:34,570
I'm pregnant.

941
00:58:54,580 --> 00:58:56,710
What did you just say?

942
00:58:58,950 --> 00:59:02,440
Did I hear right?

943
00:59:03,350 --> 00:59:06,420
I didn't imagine it, did I?

944
00:59:06,430 --> 00:59:08,610
I thought you should know.

945
00:59:22,660 --> 00:59:26,050
<i>Rudolph the red nosed reindeer</i>

946
00:59:26,060 --> 00:59:29,220
<i>Had a very shiny nose</i>

947
00:59:29,220 --> 00:59:32,110
<i>And if you ever saw it...</i>

948
00:59:32,120 --> 00:59:33,210
Merry Christmas!

949
00:59:33,220 --> 00:59:34,520
Hello.

950
00:59:34,530 --> 00:59:35,940
Yes, hello.

951
00:59:44,660 --> 00:59:48,050
Oh, my! This is crazy!

952
00:59:49,260 --> 00:59:51,070
Do you like it?

953
00:59:51,080 --> 00:59:53,150
Of course.

954
00:59:53,160 --> 00:59:54,650
How do I look?

955
00:59:54,660 --> 00:59:56,250
Perfect, right?

956
00:59:57,790 --> 01:00:00,550
I was in the Miss Korea pageant.

957
01:00:03,350 --> 01:00:05,840
Let's go.
We should have a party.

958
01:00:05,850 --> 01:00:07,710
I'm so happy.

959
01:00:07,720 --> 01:00:10,210
What was that?
There is some hormone.

960
01:00:10,220 --> 01:00:13,410
Anyway, I'm filled with lots of it.

961
01:00:13,430 --> 01:00:16,320
Why don't they give hormones easy names?

962
01:00:16,330 --> 01:00:18,180
So I could remember it.

963
01:00:20,680 --> 01:00:23,170
Aeji, this is from your future uncle.

964
01:00:23,180 --> 01:00:24,870
Thank him later.

965
01:00:24,890 --> 01:00:26,720
Okay, aunt.

966
01:00:26,720 --> 01:00:29,840
Lucky you! You got a gift from your uncle.

967
01:00:29,850 --> 01:00:31,710
I don't need any gifts.

968
01:00:31,720 --> 01:00:35,070
I just want Haebak to get accepted into a good school.

969
01:00:35,080 --> 01:00:37,440
Did you send your application?

970
01:00:37,450 --> 01:00:38,710
Yes.

971
01:00:38,720 --> 01:00:41,750
Aeji, call your dad.
Tell him to hurry home.

972
01:00:41,760 --> 01:00:43,810
When is Seoul National University sending acceptance letters?

973
01:00:43,830 --> 01:00:45,850
Not for a while.

974
01:00:47,490 --> 01:00:49,840
He must be really busy tonight.

975
01:00:49,850 --> 01:00:51,980
Don said he's really busy, too.

976
01:00:51,990 --> 01:00:53,070
I heard.

977
01:00:53,080 --> 01:00:55,170
Oh, how about Subak?

978
01:00:55,180 --> 01:00:58,040
She said she's coming after her meeting.

979
01:00:58,060 --> 01:00:59,580
Dad.

980
01:01:00,330 --> 01:01:01,780
Yes, Aeji.

981
01:01:01,790 --> 01:01:03,420
Dad will come home right after I'm done.

982
01:01:03,430 --> 01:01:06,980
Dad, I'm putting aunt on the phone.

983
01:01:06,990 --> 01:01:09,480
Minjung, are you coming home late?

984
01:01:09,490 --> 01:01:12,280
I'm trying to hurry up, but I might be.

985
01:01:12,290 --> 01:01:15,480
This is my last Christmas at home.

986
01:01:15,490 --> 01:01:17,520
You should be here.

987
01:01:17,530 --> 01:01:19,780
Of course I'll be there.

988
01:01:19,790 --> 01:01:21,420
Did Subak come home?

989
01:01:22,530 --> 01:01:24,570
Okay.

990
01:01:29,580 --> 01:01:30,880
Thank you for the gift.

991
01:01:30,890 --> 01:01:32,320
I kept my promise.

992
01:01:32,330 --> 01:01:34,650
You're a true man.

993
01:01:34,660 --> 01:01:37,980
And that's why I fell in love with you.

994
01:01:37,990 --> 01:01:40,550
Who's been calling you?

995
01:01:40,560 --> 01:01:41,780
My husband wants me home.

996
01:01:41,790 --> 01:01:42,920
Answer it.

997
01:01:45,080 --> 01:01:47,710
- What is it?
- Where are you?

998
01:01:47,720 --> 01:01:49,370
At the office.

999
01:01:49,390 --> 01:01:50,420
I'm in a meeting.

1000
01:01:50,430 --> 01:01:52,220
Aeji's been calling me about

1001
01:01:52,220 --> 01:01:54,210
having a party at home.

1002
01:01:54,220 --> 01:01:55,670
Can you go home now?

1003
01:01:55,680 --> 01:01:56,940
But I'm working!

1004
01:01:56,950 --> 01:01:58,310
I'm really busy.

1005
01:01:58,330 --> 01:01:59,950
- I'm hanging up.
- Subak!

1006
01:02:14,080 --> 01:02:15,670
Minjung.

1007
01:02:24,180 --> 01:02:25,710
Hello.

1008
01:02:27,490 --> 01:02:28,710
I better go.

1009
01:02:36,330 --> 01:02:38,780
are you crazy?
Why did you hit him?

1010
01:02:44,720 --> 01:02:46,110
I want a divorce!

1011
01:02:47,830 --> 01:02:49,520
Fine.

1012
01:02:50,390 --> 01:02:51,610
Let's get a divorce.

1013
01:02:54,160 --> 01:03:10,990
Subtitles by KBS World

1014
01:03:10,990 --> 01:03:13,340
It's not much but I tried my best.

1015
01:03:13,350 --> 01:03:14,840
You think I'm an idiot?

1016
01:03:14,850 --> 01:03:15,980
I have a confession to make.

1017
01:03:15,990 --> 01:03:18,480
I get scared when you say that.

1018
01:03:18,490 --> 01:03:19,550
Is everything okay at home?

1019
01:03:19,560 --> 01:03:21,020
Nobody's been calling or dropping by?

1020
01:03:21,030 --> 01:03:22,750
No, why?

1021
01:03:22,760 --> 01:03:24,320
Why are you sitting so close together?

1022
01:03:24,330 --> 01:03:26,780
You look great together, sitting side by side.

1023
01:03:26,790 --> 01:03:28,950
Don't associate with Loser.

1024
01:03:28,950 --> 01:03:30,140
How can this happen?

1025
01:03:30,160 --> 01:03:31,880
How can they send this?

1026
01:03:31,890 --> 01:03:33,280
Daese, calm down.

1027
01:03:33,290 --> 01:03:34,680
I can't calm down! I won't!

1028
01:03:34,680 --> 01:03:38,020
Father, I'm getting a divorce.

